quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,"Pellet, kayre ko nde peewal e Yurmeende wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  27,78,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa O √Īaawirat hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Ďaawoore makko ngal, ko KaŇčko woni Teddu…óo ganndu…óo."
  27,79,"Wakkilo e Alla, pellet, an ha…óa e hoore Goonga …ďannguka ka."
  27,80,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maay…ďe …ďen, a nanintaa fa'a…óu…ďe …ďen noddaandu ndun si …ďe …óuurnike …ďe nduŇčitii."
  27,81,"An a wonaani peewnoowo wum…ďe …ďen e ga majjere ma…ď…ďe nde. A nanintaa si wonaa …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ďe ko …ďe jebbilii…ďe."
  27,82,"Si konngol ngol yanii e dow ma…ď…ďe, Min yaltinana …ďe daabewa immorde ka leydi himba kaalana …ďe won'nde yim…ďe …ďen laatike …ďe yananaaka aayeeje Amen …óen."
  27,83,"E √Īande Min moo…ďoyta immorde e kala mofte dental jeyaa…ďe e …ďen yennoo…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen hara kam…ďe he…ďe coggee."
  27,84,"Haa si …ďe ngarii, O Daala: "Eyoo, on yenniino Aayeeje Am …óen, hara on hu…ďindoraali …ói ganndal. Kaa ko hol…óum won…óon e gollude?""
  27,85,"Konngol [Lepte] ngol yani e ma…ď…ďe sabu ko …ďe too√Īi ko, kam…ďe …ďe kaalataa."
  27,86,"Enee, hara …ďe yiaani, Minen Min mba…óii jemma on fii yo …ďe dee∆īu e maako, e √Īalawma on nji'ir…óo? Pellet, wonii e …óum Aayeeje wonan'de yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe …ďen."
  27,87,"E √Ďande wuttoytee ka alaadu, …óen∆īoo …ďen won…ďe ka kammuuli e …ďen won…ďe ka leydi, si wonaa …ďen …ďe Alla muuyi, gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe aray e makko hara ko …ďe hoykinii…ďe."
  27,88,"Ha…óa tina pelle …óen, cikka ko …óe fenndii…óe, hara le kannje he…óe wuloo wulagol duule …óen, …óuum ko kuugal Alla, On Ňčar…óin…óo kala hu'unde, pellet, KaŇčko ko O kumpitii…óo ko ngolloton kon."